specifications.Finish: Decoration > Embroidery Embroidery is a decorative finishing that uses different stitches, yarns, and materials to create patterns on the fabric. This process adds visual interest, texture, and a handcrafted feel.
specifications.Dye Method: Printed - Appearance > Scalloped Scalloped edges feature a series of rounded, wave-like curves along fabric hems or trims, adding a delicate and elegant detail that enhances the garment's overall appearance.
specifications.Care Instructions: Hand wash only Wash separately Turn inside out before washing, Do not wring, Do not rub Do not bleach Line dry Do not tumble dry Iron on low heat on reverse side if needed Recommended Use Dresses
